honline\/2016\/12\/03\/accept-divine-decree\/","url_meta":{"origin":39728,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Qadr: Believers must accept the Divine Decree","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 3, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cA servant does not have faith until he believes in divine providence, both its good and its harm, and until he knows that what afflicts him could never have missed him and what missed him\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39801,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/19\/abu-darda-peak-iman\/","url_meta":{"origin":39728,"position":1},"title":"Abu Darda on Qadr: Peak of faith is acceptance of Allah\u2019s decree","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 19, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Lalaka\u2019i reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cThe pinnacle of faith is in four things: patience with the judgment of Allah, pleasure with the decree of Allah, sincerity and trust in Allah, and surrender to the Lord.\u201d Source: Sharh\u0323 Us\u0323u\u0304l I\u2019tiqa\u0304d Ahl al-Sunnah wal-Jama\u0304\u2019ah 1697 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39828,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/20\/contentment-jannah-dunya\/","url_meta":{"origin":39728,"position":2},"title":"Abdul Wahid on Contentment: Pleasure with Allah\u2019s decree is Paradise of this world","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 20, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Sarri ibn Hassan reported: Abdul Wahid ibn Zayd, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cContentment is one of the greatest doors to Allah, the Paradise of this world, and the repose of the worshipers.\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304' 6\/156 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0633\u064e\u0651\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u062d\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0648\u064e\u0627\u062d\u0650\u062f\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u064f \u0632\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u064d \u0631\u064e\u062d\u0650\u0645\u064e\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39808,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/19\/accepting-death\/","url_meta":{"origin":39728,"position":3},"title":"Ibn Umar on Qadr: Accepting Allah\u2019s decree at death of a beloved","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 19, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Nafi\u2019 reported: A son of Abdullah ibn Umar, may Allah be pleased with him, complained of an illness and Ibn Umar was very distraught over him so much that some people said: We are afraid for this old man because of what might happen to his boy! The boy died\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39766,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/18\/ali-rida-qadr\/","url_meta":{"origin":39728,"position":4},"title":"Ali on Qadr: Acceptance of Allah\u2019s decree even if unpleasant","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 18, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Agharr reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, upon him be peace, saw \u2018Adi ibn Hatim in dismay. Ali said, \u201cO \u2018Adi, what is wrong that I see you sad and distressed?\u201d \u2018Adi said, \u201cWhy should I not be when my sons have been killed and my eye has been gouged?\u201d Ali\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35292,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/02\/22\/umar-content-decree\/","url_meta":{"origin":39728,"position":5},"title":"Umar II on Qadr: O Allah, make me satisfied with the Decree","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 22, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Yahya ibn Sa\u2019id reported: Umar ibn Abdul Aziz, may Allah be pleased with him, used to say, \u201cO Allah, make me content with Your providence and bless me in Your decree, such that I would not like to hasten what has been delayed, nor delay what has been hastened.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\